WEBVTT

1
01:16:22.160 --> 01:16:26.540 
在我寂寞的时候 你来找我 真是太好了
It's so kind of you to visit me in my loneliness.

2
01:16:27.950 --> 01:16:30.750 
你想把我的狗怎么样 把它还给我
What are you gonna do with my dog? Give him back to me.

3
01:16:30.920 --> 01:16:33.380 
等时间到了再说 小美人
All in good time, my little pretty.

4
01:16:33.540 --> 01:16:37.510 
-一切都来的很及时 -求求你把狗还给我
- All in good time. - Please give me back my dog.

5
01:16:37.670 --> 01:16:40.010 
当然 当然
Certainly, certainly...

6
01:16:40.180 --> 01:16:43.140 
当你把仙鞋给我时
...when you give me those slippers.

7
01:16:43.300 --> 01:16:47.140 
-但是好女巫让我不要给你 -很好
- But the Good Witch told me not to. - Very well.

8
01:16:47.310 --> 01:16:49.480 
把篮子扔进河里淹死它
Throw that basket in the river and drown him.

9
01:16:49.640 --> 01:16:53.770 
不 不要 你可以把仙鞋拿去 但托托要还给我
No. Here. You can have your old slippers, but give me back Toto.

10
01:16:53.940 --> 01:16:55.610 
是个好女孩
That's a good little girl.

